description: Certified models meet all ENERGY STAR requirements as listed in the Version 3.0 ENERGY STAR Program Requirements for Dehumidifiers that are effective as of October 1, 2012. A detailed listing of key efficiency criteria are available at http://www.energystar.gov/index.cfm?c=dehumid.pr_crit_dehumidifiers
